org.apache.mesos.dcos

Class DcosVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.mesos.dcos.DcosVersion

  • public class DcosVersion
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the response from a DC/OS cluster's dcos-metadata/dcos-version.json endpoint. Example response: HTTP/1.1 200 OK Accept-Ranges: bytes Connection: keep-alive Content-Length: 154 Content-Type: application/json Date: Thu, 28 Jul 2016 17:57:48 GMT ETag: "5797a2e7-9a" Last-Modified: Tue, 26 Jul 2016 17:50:31 GMT Server: openresty/1.7.10.2 { "bootstrap-id": "27f0ee12ec563574dd9a6fa93faba1a1be38bde5", "dcos-image-commit": "3fe4305af8ab9b4c2c3606569f3c0cb5c5437aa3", "version": "1.7.3" }
